title: Foreign Aid Worker In Singapore
description: There are not too many true country girls left. Most have moved to the big city, become urbanised and sophisticated. But Chonabot is pure country. Dark fit figure, well used to work. Long toned legs, so she does not sink too deep in the rice fields. Does what she is told, complicit and gives good service. Does not want much money either. That is going to change. But so far, real country morality, do a day's work, get a day's pay. Give her a week in the city and it will all change. Do a day's work, get a new brand name pocket book. In the mean time, what the Chonabot get off the bus and get right into the HD video
